sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>gRPC Client
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Adapter as runtime-adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer/TorchServe)

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Loading (Puller + Adapter)

    MM->>Puller: loadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8084/TCP
    activate Puller

    Puller->>Puller: Parse storage config from<br/>/storage-config mount

    Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials (S3/GCS/Azure)
    activate Storage
    Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    deactivate Storage

    Puller->>Puller: Write artifacts to<br/>/models/{modelId}

    Puller->>Adapter: loadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP
    activate Adapter

    alt Triton Adapter
        Adapter->>Adapter: Adapt model layout<br/>Generate config.pbtxt
        opt Keras model detected
            Adapter->>Adapter: tf_pb.py converts<br/>.h5 → SavedModel
        end
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad<br/>gRPC 8001/TCP plaintext
    else OVMS Adapter
        Adapter->>Adapter: Update model_config_list.json<br/>Batch reload requests
        Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload<br/>HTTP 8001/TCP plaintext
    else MLServer Adapter
        Adapter->>Adapter: Generate model-settings.json<br/>Map model type to implementation
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad<br/>gRPC 8001/TCP plaintext
    else TorchServe Adapter
        Adapter->>Adapter: Generate mmconfig.properties
        Adapter->>Runtime: RegisterModel<br/>gRPC 7071/TCP plaintext
    end

    activate Runtime
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load success + model metadata
    deactivate Runtime

    Adapter-->>Puller: loadModel response<br/>(sizeInBytes, maxConcurrency)
    deactivate Adapter

    Puller-->>MM: loadModel response
    deactivate Puller

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Loading (Embedded Puller)

    MM->>Adapter: loadModel(modelId, modelPath)<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP<br/>(USE_EMBEDDED_PULLER=true)
    activate Adapter

    Adapter->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
    activate Storage
    Storage-->>Adapter: Model artifacts
    deactivate Storage

    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model<br/>gRPC/HTTP plaintext
    activate Runtime
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load success
    deactivate Runtime

    Adapter-->>MM: loadModel response
    deactivate Adapter

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Runtime Status Check

    MM->>Adapter: runtimeStatus()<br/>gRPC plaintext 8085/TCP
    activate Adapter

    alt TorchServe
        Adapter->>Runtime: Ping<br/>gRPC 7070/TCP plaintext
    else Triton/MLServer
        Adapter->>Runtime: ServerReady<br/>gRPC 8001/TCP plaintext
    else OVMS
        Adapter->>Runtime: GET /v1/config<br/>HTTP 8001/TCP plaintext
    end

    activate Runtime
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Status response
    deactivate Runtime

    Adapter-->>MM: runtimeStatus response<br/>(status, capacityInBytes, modelCapacity)
    deactivate Adapter
